user.en:
Write a USER.md profile file for a research team AI agent.
Agent: {{agentName}} | Role: {{agentRole}}
Team: {{scenarioName}}

Write 1 sentence describing the research lead or stakeholder this agent serves — their role, research goals, and how they use findings.

Output plain markdown text only. No JSON.

user.zh:
为研究团队 AI 智能体写一份 USER.md 画像文件。
智能体：{{agentName}} | 角色：{{agentRole}}
团队：{{scenarioName}}

写1句话描述该智能体服务的研究负责人或利益相关者——其角色、研究目标和如何使用研究成果。

仅输出纯 Markdown 文本，不要 JSON。

heartbeat.en:
Write a HEARTBEAT.md checklist for a research team AI agent.
Agent: {{agentName}} | Role: {{agentRole}}
Team: {{scenarioName}}

Output 5 recurring research task checkboxes specific to this agent's analytical role.
Format: - [ ] task description

No headings, no other text.

heartbeat.zh:
